can be more elaborate too.

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:46.100
We can be in the habit of exercising

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.550
at a particular time of day.

00:00:47.550 --> 00:00:49.230
We can be in the habit
of eating certain foods.

00:00:49.230 --> 00:00:52.032
